♪ Freak out ♪

01:13:22.315 --> 01:13:24.357
♪ Le Freak, c'est chic ♪

01:13:24.442 --> 01:13:26.359
♪ Freak out ♪

01:13:27.862 --> 01:13:30.238
♪ Ahhh, freak out ♪

01:13:30.323 --> 01:13:32.407
♪ Le Freak, c'est chic ♪

01:13:32.533 --> 01:13:34.659
♪ Freak out ♪
